# JohnDovey build environment

Before Android or Gradle compiles, consult `/Volumes/JohnDovey/source-john-dovey.sh` (or `source` it). Key paths when the drive is mounted:

- `ANDROID_HOME` → `/Volumes/JohnDovey/Android/Sdk`
- `GRADLE_USER_HOME` → `/Volumes/JohnDovey/.gradle`
- `JAVA_HOME` → `/usr/local/opt/openjdk@17/libexec/openjdk.jdk/Contents/Home`

Use **`/Volumes/JohnDovey/tmp/`** for temporary build/release output — not `/tmp` on the system drive.

Full notes: `docs/CLAUDE.md`.
